
pnorm(p,v) := (abs(v[1])**p + abs(v[2])**p) ** (1/p)$

pnormalize(p,v) := v / pnorm(p,v)$

pnormal(p,v) := [abs(v[1])**(p-1)*signum(v[1]), abs(v[1])**(p-1)*signum(v[2])]$


P:4$
Q:1/(1-1/P)$

a: [-1/2, 1]$
b: [1, 1]$

u:pnormalize(P,a)$
v:pnormalize(P,b)$

d1:pnormalize(P, u-v)$
d2:pnormalize(P, u+v)$

c:pnormal(P, d1)$
d:pnormal(P, d2)$

z:pnormalize(Q, c-d),numer;
w:pnormalize(Q, c+d),numer;
